"{\"uid\": \"slate.com-culture-2024-08-olympics-gymnastics-all-around-simone-biles-rebeca-andrade-suni-lee.html\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"This is part of Slate's 2024 Olympics coverage.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 47, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slate\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5683811331597496e-26, \"text\": \"Slate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 8, \"to\": 12}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read morehere.\", \"from\": 48, \"to\": 62, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well my friends,I said it might happen, and for a few minutes there during the women's all-around gymnastics final in Paris' Bercy Arena, I thought it actually would: Simone Biles, the greatest gymnast the sport has ever seen, was brieflybehind.\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 182, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5716376370137326e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 189, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bercy Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\"}, {\"begin\": 231, \"end\": 243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few minutes\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 125}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest gymnast\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 265}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I said it, and I meant it: Brazil's Rebeca Andrade was within Biles' margin of error!\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 337, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6108273114076734, \"rank\": 0.6371159803341063, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles' margin\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"error\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after a competition filled with more twists and turns than-wait, what's a sport that features many literal twists and turns?\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a competition\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 419}, {\"ngram\": \"more twists\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"turns\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"many literal twists\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"turns\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not think of one-the all-around podium had Biles at the top, continuing her run as the most decorated American Olympic gymnast of all time.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999998198391202, \"rank\": 1.7852654013923673e